<p>Tuesday 4 December</p>
<p>Frosty and bitterly cold.<br/>Assisting in the cleaning of a motor ambulance during the morning.<br/>After dinner went in a car to the 5th Div. Workshops near Bailleul, calling at the 2nd Aust. Casualty Clearing Station near Steenwerck on the way.  Rode the motor bike back to camp.<br/>After tea took the usual Casualty wire to 15th Brigade Sigs.<br/>Fritz was over early this morning dropping bombs</p>
